Package: kontrocode
Version: 0.1.0
Section: devel
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libwebkit2gtk-4.1-0, libgtk-3-0, libglib2.0-0
Maintainer: KontroCode Team <team@kontrocode.dev>
Description: Research-first, memory-aware native coding agent
 KontroCode is a native PC coding agent that researches official docs,
 package registries, and community signals before generating code.
 .
 Built on a Zed editor fork (GPUI/Rust) with an OpenCode-style agent brain.
 Faster than Cursor, smarter than Copilot, never ships deprecated code.
